  39. (* Returns the imports required to access the structure at path p *)
  40. (* Only raises Not_found if the head of p is not in the toplevel map *)
  41. let rec lookup_free p m =
  42.   match p with
  43.     [] -> raise Not_found
  44.   | s::p ->
  45.       let Node (f, m') = String.Map.find s m  in
  46.       try lookup_free p m' with Not_found -> f

  48. (* Returns the node corresponding to the structure at path p *)
  49. ‌let rec lookup_map lid m =

  52.   | Ldot (l, s) -> String.Map.find s (get_map (lookup_map l m))

  98. ‌let rec add_type bv ty =
  99.   match ty.ptyp_desc with
  100.     Ptyp_any -> ()
  101.   | Ptyp_var _ -> ()
  102.   | Ptyp_arrow(_, t1, t2) -> add_type bv t1; add_type bv t2
  103.   | Ptyp_tuple tl -> List.iter (add_type bv) tl
  104.   | Ptyp_constr(c, tl) -> add bv c; List.iter (add_type bv) tl
  105.   | Ptyp_object (fl, _) ->
  106.       List.iter
  107.        (fun {pof_desc; _} -> match pof_desc with
  108.          | Otag (_, t) -> add_type bv t
  109.          | Oinherit t -> add_type bv t) fl
  110.   | Ptyp_class(c, tl) -> add bv c; List.iter (add_type bv) tl
  111.   | Ptyp_alias(t, _) -> add_type bv t
  112.   | Ptyp_variant(fl, _, _) ->
  113.       List.iter
  114.         (fun {prf_desc; _} -> match prf_desc with
  115.           | Rtag(_, _, stl) -> List.iter (add_type bv) stl
  116.           | Rinherit sty -> add_type bv sty)
  117.         fl
  118.   | Ptyp_poly(_, t) -> add_type bv t
  119.   | Ptyp_package pt -> add_package_type bv pt
  120.   | Ptyp_extension e -> handle_extension e

  122. and add_package_type bv (lid, l) =
  123.   add bv lid;
  124.   List.iter (add_type bv) (List.map (fun (_, e) -> e) l)

  126. let add_opt add_fn bv = function
  127.     None -> ()

  130. ‌let add_constructor_arguments bv = function

  132.   | Pcstr_record l -> List.iter (fun l -> add_type bv l.pld_type) l

  166. ‌let pattern_bv = ref String.Map.empty

  168. ‌let rec add_pattern bv pat =
  169.   match pat.ppat_desc with
  170.     Ppat_any -> ()
  171.   | Ppat_var _ -> ()
  172.   | Ppat_alias(p, _) -> add_pattern bv p
  173.   | Ppat_interval _
  174.   | Ppat_constant _ -> ()
  175.   | Ppat_tuple pl -> List.iter (add_pattern bv) pl
  176.   | Ppat_construct(c, opt) ->
  177.       add bv c;
  178.       add_opt
  179.         (fun bv (_,p) -> add_pattern bv p)
  180.         bv opt
  181.   | Ppat_record(pl, _) ->
  182.       List.iter (fun (lbl, p) -> add bv lbl; add_pattern bv p) pl
  183.   | Ppat_array pl -> List.iter (add_pattern bv) pl
  184.   | Ppat_or(p1, p2) -> add_pattern bv p1; add_pattern bv p2
  185.   | Ppat_constraint(p, ty) -> add_pattern bv p; add_type bv ty
  186.   | Ppat_variant(_, op) -> add_opt add_pattern bv op
  187.   | Ppat_type li -> add bv li
  188.   | Ppat_lazy p -> add_pattern bv p
  189.   | Ppat_unpack id ->
  190.       Option.iter
  191.         (fun name -> pattern_bv := String.Map.add name bound !pattern_bv) id.txt
  192.   | Ppat_open ( m, p) -> let bv = open_module bv m.txt in add_pattern bv p
  193.   | Ppat_exception p -> add_pattern bv p
  194.   | Ppat_extension e -> handle_extension e

  196. ‌let add_pattern bv pat =
  197.   pattern_bv := bv;
  198.   add_pattern bv pat;
  199.   !pattern_bv

  201. ‌let rec add_expr bv exp =
  202.   match exp.pexp_desc with
  203.     Pexp_ident l -> add bv l
  204.   | Pexp_constant _ -> ()
  205.   | Pexp_let(rf, pel, e) ->
  206.       let bv = add_bindings rf bv pel in add_expr bv e
  207.   | Pexp_fun (_, opte, p, e) ->
  208.       add_opt add_expr bv opte; add_expr (add_pattern bv p) e
  209.   | Pexp_function pel ->
  210.       add_cases bv pel
  211.   | Pexp_apply(e, el) ->
  212.       add_expr bv e; List.iter (fun (_,e) -> add_expr bv e) el
  213.   | Pexp_match(e, pel) -> add_expr bv e; add_cases bv pel
  214.   | Pexp_try(e, pel) -> add_expr bv e; add_cases bv pel
  215.   | Pexp_tuple el -> List.iter (add_expr bv) el
  216.   | Pexp_construct(c, opte) -> add bv c; add_opt add_expr bv opte
  217.   | Pexp_variant(_, opte) -> add_opt add_expr bv opte
  218.   | Pexp_record(lblel, opte) ->
  219.       List.iter (fun (lbl, e) -> add bv lbl; add_expr bv e) lblel;
  220.       add_opt add_expr bv opte
  221.   | Pexp_field(e, fld) -> add_expr bv e; add bv fld
  222.   | Pexp_setfield(e1, fld, e2) -> add_expr bv e1; add bv fld; add_expr bv e2
  223.   | Pexp_array el -> List.iter (add_expr bv) el
  224.   | Pexp_ifthenelse(e1, e2, opte3) ->
  225.       add_expr bv e1; add_expr bv e2; add_opt add_expr bv opte3
  226.   | Pexp_sequence(e1, e2) -> add_expr bv e1; add_expr bv e2
  227.   | Pexp_while(e1, e2) -> add_expr bv e1; add_expr bv e2
  228.   | Pexp_for( _, e1, e2, _, e3) ->
  229.       add_expr bv e1; add_expr bv e2; add_expr bv e3
  230.   | Pexp_coerce(e1, oty2, ty3) ->
  231.       add_expr bv e1;
  232.       add_opt add_type bv oty2;
  233.       add_type bv ty3
  234.   | Pexp_constraint(e1, ty2) ->
  235.       add_expr bv e1;
  236.       add_type bv ty2
  237.   | Pexp_send(e, _m) -> add_expr bv e
  238.   | Pexp_new li -> add bv li
  239.   | Pexp_setinstvar(_v, e) -> add_expr bv e
  240.   | Pexp_override sel -> List.iter (fun (_s, e) -> add_expr bv e) sel
  241.   | Pexp_letmodule(id, m, e) ->
  242.       let b = add_module_binding bv m in
  243.       let bv =
  244.         match id.txt with
  245.         | None -> bv
  246.         | Some id -> String.Map.add id b bv
  247.       in
  248.       add_expr bv e
  249.   | Pexp_letexception(_, e) -> add_expr bv e
  250.   | Pexp_assert (e) -> add_expr bv e
  251.   | Pexp_lazy (e) -> add_expr bv e
  252.   | Pexp_poly (e, t) -> add_expr bv e; add_opt add_type bv t
  253.   | Pexp_object { pcstr_self = pat; pcstr_fields = fieldl } ->
  254.       let bv = add_pattern bv pat in List.iter (add_class_field bv) fieldl
  255.   | Pexp_newtype (_, e) -> add_expr bv e
  256.   | Pexp_pack m -> add_module_expr bv m
  257.   | Pexp_open (o, e) ->
  258.       let bv = open_declaration bv o in
  259.       add_expr bv e
  260.   | Pexp_letop {let_; ands; body} ->
  261.       let bv' = add_binding_op bv bv let_ in
  262.       let bv' = List.fold_left (add_binding_op bv) bv' ands in
  263.       add_expr bv' body
  264.   | Pexp_extension (({ txt = ("ocaml.extension_constructor"|
  265.                               "extension_constructor"); _ },
  266.                      PStr [item]) as e) ->
  267.       begin match item.pstr_desc with
  268.       | Pstr_eval ({ pexp_desc = Pexp_construct (c, None) }, _) -> add bv c
  269.       | _ -> handle_extension e
  270.       end
  271.   | Pexp_extension e -> handle_extension e
  272.   | Pexp_unreachable -> ()

  274. and add_cases bv cases =
  275.   List.iter (add_case bv) cases

  277. and add_case bv {pc_lhs; pc_guard; pc_rhs} =
  278.   let bv = add_pattern bv pc_lhs in
  279.   add_opt add_expr bv pc_guard;
  280.   add_expr bv pc_rhs

  282. and add_bindings recf bv pel =
  283.   let bv' = List.fold_left (fun bv x -> add_pattern bv x.pvb_pat) bv pel in
  284.   let bv = if recf = Recursive then bv' else bv in
  285.   let add_constraint = function
  286.     | Pvc_constraint {locally_abstract_univars=_; typ} ->
  287.         add_type bv typ
  288.     | Pvc_coercion { ground; coercion } ->
  289.         Option.iter (add_type bv) ground;
  290.         add_type bv coercion
  291.   in
  292.   let add_one_binding { pvb_pat= _ ; pvb_loc= _ ; pvb_constraint; pvb_expr } =
  293.     add_expr bv pvb_expr;
  294.     Option.iter add_constraint pvb_constraint
  295.   in
  296.   List.iter add_one_binding pel;
  297.   bv'

  299. ‌and add_binding_op bv bv' pbop =
  300.   add_expr bv pbop.pbop_exp;
  301.   add_pattern bv' pbop.pbop_pat

  303. and add_modtype bv mty =
  304.   match mty.pmty_desc with
  305.     Pmty_ident l -> add bv l
  306.   | Pmty_alias l -> add_module_path bv l
  307.   | Pmty_signature s -> add_signature bv s
  308.   | Pmty_functor(param, mty2) ->
  309.       let bv =
  310.         match param with
  311.         | Unit -> bv
  312.         | Named (id, mty1) ->
  313.           add_modtype bv mty1;
  314.           match id.txt with
  315.           | None -> bv
  316.           | Some name -> String.Map.add name bound bv
  317.       in
  318.       add_modtype bv mty2
  319.   | Pmty_with(mty, cstrl) ->
  320.       add_modtype bv mty;
  321.       List.iter
  322.         (function
  323.           | Pwith_type (_, td) -> add_type_declaration bv td
  324.           | Pwith_module (_, lid) -> add_module_path bv lid
  325.           | Pwith_modtype (_, mty) -> add_modtype bv mty
  326.           | Pwith_typesubst (_, td) -> add_type_declaration bv td
  327.           | Pwith_modsubst (_, lid) -> add_module_path bv lid
  328.           | Pwith_modtypesubst (_, mty) -> add_modtype bv mty
  329.         )
  330.         cstrl
  331.   | Pmty_typeof m -> add_module_expr bv m
  332.   | Pmty_extension e -> handle_extension e

  334. and add_module_alias bv l =
  335.   (* If we are in delayed dependencies mode, we delay the dependencies
  336.        induced by "Lident s" *)
  337.   (if !Clflags.transparent_modules then add_parent else add_module_path) bv l;
  338.   try
  339.     lookup_map l.txt bv
  340.   with Not_found ->
  341.     match l.txt with
  342.       Lident s -> make_leaf s
  343.     | _ -> add_module_path bv l; bound (* cannot delay *)

  345. and add_modtype_binding bv mty =
  346.   match mty.pmty_desc with
  347.     Pmty_alias l ->
  348.       add_module_alias bv l
  349.   | Pmty_signature s ->
  350.       make_node (add_signature_binding bv s)
  351.   | Pmty_typeof modl ->
  352.       add_module_binding bv modl
  353.   | _ ->
  354.       add_modtype bv mty; bound

  356. and add_signature bv sg =
  357.   ignore (add_signature_binding bv sg)

  359. and add_signature_binding bv sg =
  360.   snd (List.fold_left add_sig_item (bv, String.Map.empty) sg)

  362. and add_sig_item (bv, m) item =
  363.   match item.psig_desc with
  364.     Psig_value vd ->
  365.       add_type bv vd.pval_type; (bv, m)
  366.   | Psig_type (_, dcls)
  367.   | Psig_typesubst dcls->
  368.       List.iter (add_type_declaration bv) dcls; (bv, m)
  369.   | Psig_typext te ->
  370.       add_type_extension bv te; (bv, m)
  371.   | Psig_exception te ->
  372.       add_type_exception bv te; (bv, m)
  373.   | Psig_module pmd ->
  374.       let m' = add_modtype_binding bv pmd.pmd_type in
  375.       let add map =
  376.         match pmd.pmd_name.txt with
  377.         | None -> map
  378.         | Some name -> String.Map.add name m' map
  379.       in
  380.       (add bv, add m)
  381.   | Psig_modsubst pms ->
  382.       let m' = add_module_alias bv pms.pms_manifest in
  383.       let add = String.Map.add pms.pms_name.txt m' in
  384.       (add bv, add m)
  385.   | Psig_recmodule decls ->
  386.       let add =
  387.         List.fold_right (fun pmd map ->
  388.           match pmd.pmd_name.txt with
  389.           | None -> map
  390.           | Some name -> String.Map.add name bound map
  391.         ) decls
  392.       in
  393.       let bv' = add bv and m' = add m in
  394.       List.iter (fun pmd -> add_modtype bv' pmd.pmd_type) decls;
  395.       (bv', m')
  396.   | Psig_modtype x | Psig_modtypesubst x->
  397.       begin match x.pmtd_type with
  398.         None -> ()
  399.       | Some mty -> add_modtype bv mty
  400.       end;
  401.       (bv, m)
  402.   | Psig_open od ->
  403.       (open_description bv od, m)
  404.   | Psig_include incl ->
  405.       let Node (s, m') = add_modtype_binding bv incl.pincl_mod in
  406.       add_names s;
  407.       let add = String.Map.fold String.Map.add m' in
  408.       (add bv, add m)
  409.   | Psig_class cdl ->
  410.       List.iter (add_class_description bv) cdl; (bv, m)
  411.   | Psig_class_type cdtl ->
  412.       List.iter (add_class_type_declaration bv) cdtl; (bv, m)
  413.   | Psig_attribute _ -> (bv, m)
  414.   | Psig_extension (e, _) ->
  415.       handle_extension e;
  416.       (bv, m)

  418. and open_description bv od =
  419.   let Node(s, m) = add_module_alias bv od.popen_expr in
  420.   add_names s;
  421.   String.Map.fold String.Map.add m bv

  423. and open_declaration bv od =
  424.   let Node (s, m) = add_module_binding bv od.popen_expr in
  425.   add_names s;
  426.   String.Map.fold String.Map.add m bv

  428. and add_module_binding bv modl =
  429.   match modl.pmod_desc with
  430.     Pmod_ident l -> add_module_alias bv l
  431.   | Pmod_structure s ->
  432.      make_node (snd @@ add_structure_binding bv s)
  433.   | _ -> add_module_expr bv modl; bound

  435. and add_module_expr bv modl =
  436.   match modl.pmod_desc with
  437.     Pmod_ident l -> add_module_path bv l
  438.   | Pmod_structure s -> ignore (add_structure bv s)
  439.   | Pmod_functor(param, modl) ->
  440.       let bv =
  441.         match param with
  442.         | Unit -> bv
  443.         | Named (id, mty) ->
  444.           add_modtype bv mty;
  445.           match id.txt with
  446.           | None -> bv
  447.           | Some name -> String.Map.add name bound bv
  448.       in
  449.       add_module_expr bv modl
  450.   | Pmod_apply (mod1, mod2) ->
  451.       add_module_expr bv mod1;
  452.       add_module_expr bv mod2
  453.   | Pmod_apply_unit mod1 ->
  454.       add_module_expr bv mod1
  455.   | Pmod_constraint(modl, mty) ->
  456.       add_module_expr bv modl; add_modtype bv mty
  457.   | Pmod_unpack(e) ->
  458.       add_expr bv e
  459.   | Pmod_extension e ->
  460.       handle_extension e

  462. and add_class_type bv cty =
  463.   match cty.pcty_desc with
  464.     Pcty_constr(l, tyl) ->
  465.       add bv l; List.iter (add_type bv) tyl
  466.   | Pcty_signature { pcsig_self = ty; pcsig_fields = fieldl } ->
  467.       add_type bv ty;
  468.       List.iter (add_class_type_field bv) fieldl
  469.   | Pcty_arrow(_, ty1, cty2) ->
  470.       add_type bv ty1; add_class_type bv cty2
  471.   | Pcty_extension e -> handle_extension e
  472.   | Pcty_open (o, e) ->
  473.       let bv = open_description bv o in
  474.       add_class_type bv e

  476. and add_class_type_field bv pctf =
  477.   match pctf.pctf_desc with
  478.     Pctf_inherit cty -> add_class_type bv cty
  479.   | Pctf_val(_, _, _, ty) -> add_type bv ty
  480.   | Pctf_method(_, _, _, ty) -> add_type bv ty
  481.   | Pctf_constraint(ty1, ty2) -> add_type bv ty1; add_type bv ty2
  482.   | Pctf_attribute _ -> ()
  483.   | Pctf_extension e -> handle_extension e

  485. and add_class_description bv infos =
  486.   add_class_type bv infos.pci_expr

  488. and add_class_type_declaration bv infos = add_class_description bv infos

  490. and add_structure bv item_list =
  491.   let (bv, m) = add_structure_binding bv item_list in
  492.   add_names (collect_free (make_node m));
  493.   bv

  495. and add_structure_binding bv item_list =
  496.   List.fold_left add_struct_item (bv, String.Map.empty) item_list

  498. and add_struct_item (bv, m) item : _ String.Map.t * _ String.Map.t =
  499.   match item.pstr_desc with
  500.     Pstr_eval (e, _attrs) ->
  501.       add_expr bv e; (bv, m)
  502.   | Pstr_value(rf, pel) ->
  503.       let bv = add_bindings rf bv pel in (bv, m)
  504.   | Pstr_primitive vd ->
  505.       add_type bv vd.pval_type; (bv, m)
  506.   | Pstr_type (_, dcls) ->
  507.       List.iter (add_type_declaration bv) dcls; (bv, m)
  508.   | Pstr_typext te ->
  509.       add_type_extension bv te;
  510.       (bv, m)
  511.   | Pstr_exception te ->
  512.       add_type_exception bv te;
  513.       (bv, m)
  514.   | Pstr_module x ->
  515.       let b = add_module_binding bv x.pmb_expr in
  516.       let add map =
  517.         match x.pmb_name.txt with
  518.         | None -> map
  519.         | Some name -> String.Map.add name b map
  520.       in
  521.       (add bv, add m)
  522.   | Pstr_recmodule bindings ->
  523.       let add =
  524.         List.fold_right (fun x map ->
  525.           match x.pmb_name.txt with
  526.           | None -> map
  527.           | Some name -> String.Map.add name bound map
  528.         ) bindings
  529.       in
  530.       let bv' = add bv and m = add m in
  531.       List.iter
  532.         (fun x -> add_module_expr bv' x.pmb_expr)
  533.         bindings;
  534.       (bv', m)
  535.   | Pstr_modtype x ->
  536.       begin match x.pmtd_type with
  537.         None -> ()
  538.       | Some mty -> add_modtype bv mty
  539.       end;
  540.       (bv, m)
  541.   | Pstr_open od ->
  542.       (open_declaration bv od, m)
  543.   | Pstr_class cdl ->
  544.       List.iter (add_class_declaration bv) cdl; (bv, m)
  545.   | Pstr_class_type cdtl ->
  546.       List.iter (add_class_type_declaration bv) cdtl; (bv, m)
  547.   | Pstr_include incl ->
  548.       let Node (s, m') as n = add_module_binding bv incl.pincl_mod in
  549.       if !Clflags.transparent_modules then
  550.         add_names s
  551.       else
  552.         (* If we are not in the delayed dependency mode, we need to
  553.            collect all delayed dependencies imported by the include statement *)
  554.         add_names (collect_free n);
  555.       let add = String.Map.fold String.Map.add m' in
  556.       (add bv, add m)
  557.   | Pstr_attribute _ -> (bv, m)
  558.   | Pstr_extension (e, _) ->
  559.       handle_extension e;
  560.       (bv, m)

  562. and add_use_file bv top_phrs =
  563.   ignore (List.fold_left add_top_phrase bv top_phrs)

  565. and add_implementation bv l =
  566.     ignore (add_structure_binding bv l)

  568. and add_implementation_binding bv l =
  569.   snd (add_structure_binding bv l)

  571. and add_top_phrase bv = function
  572.   | Ptop_def str -> add_structure bv str
  573.   | Ptop_dir _ -> bv

  575. and add_class_expr bv ce =
  576.   match ce.pcl_desc with
  577.     Pcl_constr(l, tyl) ->
  578.       add bv l; List.iter (add_type bv) tyl
  579.   | Pcl_structure { pcstr_self = pat; pcstr_fields = fieldl } ->
  580.       let bv = add_pattern bv pat in List.iter (add_class_field bv) fieldl
  581.   | Pcl_fun(_, opte, pat, ce) ->
  582.       add_opt add_expr bv opte;
  583.       let bv = add_pattern bv pat in add_class_expr bv ce
  584.   | Pcl_apply(ce, exprl) ->
  585.       add_class_expr bv ce; List.iter (fun (_,e) -> add_expr bv e) exprl
  586.   | Pcl_let(rf, pel, ce) ->
  587.       let bv = add_bindings rf bv pel in add_class_expr bv ce
  588.   | Pcl_constraint(ce, ct) ->
  589.       add_class_expr bv ce; add_class_type bv ct
  590.   | Pcl_extension e -> handle_extension e
  591.   | Pcl_open (o, e) ->
  592.       let bv = open_description bv o in
  593.       add_class_expr bv e

  595. and add_class_field bv pcf =
  596.   match pcf.pcf_desc with
  597.     Pcf_inherit(_, ce, _) -> add_class_expr bv ce
  598.   | Pcf_val(_, _, Cfk_concrete (_, e))
  599.   | Pcf_method(_, _, Cfk_concrete (_, e)) -> add_expr bv e
  600.   | Pcf_val(_, _, Cfk_virtual ty)
  601.   | Pcf_method(_, _, Cfk_virtual ty) -> add_type bv ty
  602.   | Pcf_constraint(ty1, ty2) -> add_type bv ty1; add_type bv ty2
  603.   | Pcf_initializer e -> add_expr bv e
  604.   | Pcf_attribute _ -> ()
  605.   | Pcf_extension e -> handle_extension e

  607. and add_class_declaration bv decl =
  608.   add_class_expr bv decl.pci_expr
